{"tid":1308991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好在我年代有過林慧韡同達哥","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T09:09:54.000Z","uid":272077,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48c45e8def87f7bea65ef9aae9479689766ddb52","tid":1308991,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"見呢排咁多網絡紅人Post , 有感而發.<br />\n<br />\n其實依家年齡層較低既Youtuber觀眾日日都追現時Youtube上所謂紅既Youtuber,我覺得真係好可憐.<br />\n<br />\n最近有日我姪仔黎我屋企,問我拎個wifi pw 黎睇youtube .<br />\n我好奇問佢睇開咩片,佢答呀軒 同 波子 ,我本人唔太熟呢家紅果班youtuber ,但佢所講既波子 我係連登成日見  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我估無錯啦掛.<br />\n之後佢一手開撚左條PlayerUnknown既打機片, 迫我係隔離聽左半個鐘 全程都係[哇哇哇嘩 哎呀 死左啦 呢邊呢邊] <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌,原來佢係睇番D直播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n跟手我問佢 我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真實對白)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :點解你唔簡D精華片睇?通常呢D打機片都有.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :無, 佢出D片我全部都睇曬, 同埋睇佢玩足好好睇 好搞笑.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :哦...咁有咩好笑?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 佢把聲同講D野好好笑 死果陣好搞笑 (笑住黎講) 一齊睇 睇下你就知.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :.... 唔洗啦 你慢慢.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個人而言又唔會直接屌呢班Youtuber 係垃圾 , 始終時代變,風氣唔同. <br />\n有巴打用過放學ICU去比喻Youtube 我好認同 ,<br />\n我細個睇 eminleo 達哥 cookinghayhay lou記 伍公子 Ming仔 大 果陣Youtube先岩岩興起 <br />\n(唔好問點解唔睇外國既 , 正常小學/初中 唔會識得多英文 睇黎都冇意思) <br />\n佢依家就睇笑波子 大J 咩呀軒 .......(唔識 , 數唔到)<br />\n其實大家都一樣,只係睇番適逄自己年代既野. <br />\n<br />\n我唔認為我既年代既youtuber 係最好 ,但至少我認識完依家班Youtuber. 我好慶幸我唔係呢個年代出世.<br />\n<br />\n有比較先有高低, 香港直播打機/片黎講, 問心 無人高質過林慧韡同達哥 .<br />\n依家班小朋友我敢肯定唔會識得Leo/lou記既On9野 , 佢地童年就此少咁左一份有趣事."},{"pid":"9d167a5e5a619faae20560a3e78495214fe46151","tid":1308991,"uid":205043,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"sorry，大J高汁過达狗好多"},{"pid":"90d7b486e41b9efc2be5dfc625e1b736112271f5","tid":1308991,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"一蟹不如一蟹"},{"pid":"61935d60ae714b77d00b3ff22533332dc597b050","tid":1308991,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d167a5e5a619faae20560a3e78495214fe46151","tid":1308991,"uid":205043,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"sorry，大J高汁過达狗好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"達哥一直有關注"},{"pid":"3fae18d1b4f6bfaeff01c7b2512a44bd7921aa14","tid":1308991,"uid":207206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"林慧韡同達哥，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1a540953319d2a11108c76e5319fcbb2e40e2f","tid":1308991,"uid":278947,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}